            STAF BEAKER SERVICE

1. Description
This BEAKERLIB.pm is a STAF service written by Perl.

2. Confiure & Run
Step:
    1) Add the following lines into STAF.cfg
"SERVICE BEAKER LIBRARY PLSTAF EXECUTE BEAKERLIB \
            OPTION USELIB=/path/to/STAF/services"

    2) Copy BEAKERLIB.pm to the USELIB(/path/to/STAF/services)
    3) Run STAFProc
    4) Run "staf local beakerlib help" to test 

3. Usage
# Print help
staf local beakerlib help
# Print version
staf local beakerlib version
# List all beakerlib functions
staf local beakerlib list
# List some group of beakerlib functions
staf local beakerlib list "Logging" "Info"


